The '''Church of the First Frequency''' was a cult of religious fanatics.

==History==
The Church was driven off [[Otranto]] by [[Grand Inquisitor/Legends|Grand Inquisitor]] [[Laddinare Torbin]] early in the era of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Angry, the survivors of the Church decided to [[Assassin/Legends|assassinate]] Torbin, and followed him to the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]], where an attractive [[Gender/Legends|female]] cultist lured him toward a variable-gravity swimming pool. She pushed him and his [[Bodyguard/Legends|bodyguard]] into the pool, while other cultists increased the strength of the [[Force field/Legends|force field]], sealing it, and faking a [[Radiation/Legends|radiation]] leak drill to prevent others from realizing what was happening. Unfortunately for the Church survivors, [[Odumin]] managed to rescue the Grand Inquisitor. Despite this, Torbin was assassinated the next month on [[Weerden]].

